OL,3,CCarer who helped husband play football
OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,FA Newcastle carer who helped her
OL,7,Ffootball-loving husband play again
OL,8,Ffollowing a brain injury has been
OL,9,Fnominated for a national award.
OL,11,FSue Giles, 65, has cared for her 69-
OL,12,Fyear-old husband Dave for the last 18
OL,13,Fyears in a range of ways, including
OL,14,Fassisting him during walking football
OL,15,Fsessions.
OL,17,FIt has meant the Newcastle United fan
OL,18,Fhas been able to keep playing the game
OL,19,Fhe loves.
