OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Sue said the nomination was
OL,7,Fa great surprise: "It's lovely, but I
OL,8,Fwas totally taken back when I was
OL,9,Ftold. It's nice to know that somebody
OL,10,Fappreciates what you're doing because
OL,11,Fthere is a lot more to it than your
OL,12,Feveryday general life."
OL,14,FSue is one of three finalists up for
OL,15,Fthe award in London on Thursday night
OL,16,F(5 December).
